fields.subject: good
fields.content: Before I start just wanted to mention that no one encouraged me to leave this review. I Received these may 14 and to be honest my first impression on them Was that I felt like I wasted my money but I realized I didn’t put them in correctly. They are really big and look kinda awkward. Once I looked at the pic on the box of how it should look in my ear and changing the ear tip I quickly realized these headphones are pretty damn good. Great sharp bass and sound the only drawback is the mids are taken for a backseat on this one. Battery is excellent, Its made for workouts and it stays in your ear. As far as a great fit goes this one takes the cake with other buds I’ve used. I also own the AirPod pros and Jabra Active elite 75t so I have a decent sense of what sounds good. These are definitely a must buy for what you get if you didn’t wanna invest in a little more for those noise canceling premium buds. The longer I listened to These with different genres of music I Can really appreciate them for what they are.
